From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
Date: Thu, 2 Apr 2026 12:08:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] u-boot: sunxi: restore vontar-h618 legacy EMAC clock writes

Carry over the historical raw clock/register writes used by the older
H616 Vontar U-Boot LAN bring-up path.

Assisted-by: Artjom W. <aco.art@gmail.com>
---
 arch/arm/mach-sunxi/clock_sun50i_h6.c | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm/mach-sunxi/clock_sun50i_h6.c b/arch/arm/mach-sunxi/clock_sun50i_h6.c
index 7926394cf76..7c84d731f84 100644
--- a/arch/arm/mach-sunxi/clock_sun50i_h6.c
+++ b/arch/arm/mach-sunxi/clock_sun50i_h6.c
@@ -46,6 +46,10 @@ void clock_init_safe(void)
 	 * DRAM initialization code.
 	 */
 	writel(MBUS_CLK_SRC_PLL6X2 | MBUS_CLK_M(3), &ccm->mbus_cfg);
+
+	writel(0x10001, 0x030017ac);
+	writel(0x50, 0x0300a028);
+	writel(0x20, 0x0300a040);
 }
 
 void clock_init_uart(void)
-- 
2.43.0
